headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on Special Cargo and Bunker Sell Missions
content:
Don’t let stock gather dust too long in your Special Cargo Warehouse or Gunrunning Bunker — completing Sell Missions from either business will net double the regular GTA$ sale price and RP this week.

To launch the Special Cargo Missions, players must first acquire a CEO office and then purchase Special Cargo Warehouse from their office PC through SecuroServ.
